    public class BWaypointPainter<W extends org.jxmapviewer.viewer.Waypoint>
extends org.jxmapviewer.painter.AbstractPainter<org.jxmapviewer.JXMapViewer>
    Paints waypoints on the JXMapViewer. This is an instance of Painter that only can draw on to JXMapViewers.
